    "description": "<p><strong>R.J. CROCKER CONSULTANTS PTE. LTD.</strong></p>    <p>R.J. Crocker, C.T. Consultants Pte is a firm of Consulting Civil and Structural Engineers licensed to provide Professional Engineering Services in Singapore.  The firm has incorporated into an unlimited company in 1991 and now practices as R.J. Crocker Consultants Pte Ltd.</p>    <p>The firm was established in 1984 known as R.J. Crocker, C.T. & Partners Pte Ltd formed by the amalgamation of  R.J. Crocker & Partners (UK) with C.T. Consultants of Singapore.</p>    <p>We are ISO certified for ISO 9001-2008 & ISO 14001-2004, and was awarded with prestigious Goverment infrastructure projects.</p>  ",
